Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.64,0:00:03.31,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.97,0:00:05.52,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.52,0:00:08.24,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I just saw someone suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.24,0:00:10.24,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,What? Wh-What did they look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.24,0:00:13.62,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Um, he was really big, like a bear,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.62,0:00:15.97,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,with really shaggy hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.97,0:00:16.62,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Shaggy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.85,0:00:20.29,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,And he had eyes like a beast, \Ntargeting its prey!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.72,0:00:24.00,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be anything but a bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.47,0:00:38.05,ShowTitle,Title,0000,0000,0000,,Interviews with Monster Girls
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.68,0:02:04.64,Default - italics,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Someone is sitting in the hallway, crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.32,0:02:09.77,Default - italics,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,That looks like a school uniform, \Nbut not this school's...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.37,0:02:12.44,Default - italics,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,And such nice blond hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.80,0:02:16.44,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.05,0:02:21.25,Default - italics,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.37,0:02:24.91,Title1,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,600)}Succubus-san Is Inquisitive
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.94,0:02:24.91,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Satou Sakie, the math teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.40,0:02:26.04,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.32,0:02:28.50,Default,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,Sakie-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.38,0:02:31.57,Default,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Kurtz.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.57,0:02:34.00,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Are you part German, by any chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.34,0:02:35.75,Default,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.75,0:02:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you could tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.52,0:02:39.08,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,A lucky guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.08,0:02:41.68,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,I happen to have studied a \Nbit of German in college.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.68,0:02:42.39,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.83,0:02:45.95,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,So what are you doing here, Kurtz-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.59,0:02:49.95,Default,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I came here with someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.95,0:02:52.01,Default,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,but we got separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.01,0:02:54.39,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Was it your parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.39,0:02:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were they filling out transfer paperwork?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.64,0:02:57.74,Default,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.99,0:02:58.88,Default,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.88,0:02:59.86,Default - italics,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't look like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.96,0:03:03.68,Default - italics,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,It looks he isn't really a transfer student,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.68,0:03:06.63,Default - italics,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,but he doesn't seem like a bad kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.63,0:03:08.04,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Satou-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.43,0:03:09.47,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.47,0:03:10.41,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.90,0:03:12.30,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.85,0:03:16.70,Default,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,That girl's head was...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.70,0:03:20.09,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, she's a demi-human. A dullahan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.32,0:03:22.77,Default,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,Really? She is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.77,0:03:25.76,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Are you interested in \Ndemi-humans, Kurtz-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.76,0:03:26.85,Default,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,No, not especially.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:28.10,Default - italics,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,He totally is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.36,0:03:30.81,Default - italics,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I should ask why he's really here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.06,0:03:34.31,Default - italics,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,But will he actually tell me the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.69,0:03:36.86,Default - italics,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,I should use my aphrodisiac \Neffect to make him talk—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.86,0:03:39.04,Default - italics,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no, no, no, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.04,0:03:42.66,Default - italics,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I suddenly thinking like that? Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.99,0:03:45.53,Default,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,Um, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.84,0:03:49.62,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go and look for your parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:51.71,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,That will probably be faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:52.12,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Off, I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.45,0:03:53.89,Default,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.08,0:03:59.51,Default - italics,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.23,0:04:04.84,Default - italics,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,The effect isn't working?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.35,0:04:09.43,Default - italics,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,That does sometimes happen with people \Nwho haven't much sexual desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.09,0:04:12.57,Default - italics,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,But he doesn't look that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.57,0:04:15.07,Default - italics,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he's actually more...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.07,0:04:16.61,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Satou-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.95,0:04:18.11,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.47,0:04:20.12,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.12,0:04:24.18,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Hikari told me she saw someone \Nsuspicious in the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.18,0:04:25.74,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Someone suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:27.64,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari saw them,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.64,0:04:30.40,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,so she may have exaggerated \Nsome of the details,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.40,0:04:32.10,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,but I wanted warn to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.10,0:04:35.23,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Suspicious... Could it have been...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.26,0:04:40.36,Default - italics,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,Sakie-sensei has such a \Nserious look on her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.36,0:04:43.55,Default - italics,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,She must be scared of the suspicious person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.55,0:04:46.65,Default - italics,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't seem to fully trust me, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.65,0:04:48.92,Default - italics,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,If I want to allay her suspicion of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.92,0:04:52.73,Default - italics,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,No, to thank her for her kindness to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.84,0:04:55.60,Default,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do something about the suspicious person!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.69,0:04:58.32,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Who's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.32,0:04:59.98,Default,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.32,0:05:01.86,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Well... His name is Kurtz-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.98,0:05:02.74,Default,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'll take that suspicious person, \Nand give 'em this and this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.86,0:05:04.78,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,He was separated from the \Npeople he came here with.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.74,0:05:04.78,Default,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You just wait, suspicious person!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:09.12,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if the suspicious person \Nshe mentioned was one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.12,0:05:10.29,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.29,0:05:13.79,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, she said the person was a \Nhuge man, who looked like a bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.10,0:05:16.76,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Someone like you, I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.76,0:05:17.17,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.65,0:05:20.34,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I'm sure he was much bigger than—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.34,0:05:21.09,Default,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,Get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.79,0:05:30.10,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:31.73,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.73,0:05:33.97,Default,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Sakie-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.97,0:05:36.81,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, that was amazing, Kurtz-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.81,0:05:39.23,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow, ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.78,0:05:41.00,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Ugaki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.28,0:05:42.15,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Ugaki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.47,0:05:43.95,Default,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,Ugaki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.16,0:05:47.78,Default,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.21,0:05:53.30,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kurtz... I thought you'd disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.30,0:05:55.62,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,What brings you here now? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.62,0:05:57.72,Default,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.72,0:05:59.29,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.72,0:05:59.29,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,He's your kouhai?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.08,0:06:04.85,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, um... He's a police detective I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.85,0:06:05.55,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,A police detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.92,0:06:08.71,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, what if you'd been wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.71,0:06:10.37,Default,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.37,0:06:12.82,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,You know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.82,0:06:16.84,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, for quite some time, you might say...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.57,0:06:21.13,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,And this boy— I mean, Kurtz-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.13,0:06:23.28,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he works for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.28,0:06:24.44,Default,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.89,0:06:28.09,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you at the school, Ugaki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.01,0:06:31.53,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess you could say...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.03,0:06:34.40,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Um, did you check in?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.40,0:06:35.70,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Check in?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:41.45,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,To enter the school, the rule is that \Nyou have to register your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.45,0:06:43.57,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.57,0:06:45.75,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Kurtz, you go do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.75,0:06:46.96,Default,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.96,0:06:49.22,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look so obviously peeved!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.68,0:06:52.13,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,He seems young for a police detective,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.13,0:06:53.93,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,and he looks foreign.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:55.24,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.50,0:06:57.91,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Guess the police force is \Npretty broad-minded...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.08,0:07:00.48,Default,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,If you'll buy me takoyaki on \Nthe way home, I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.48,0:07:02.01,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,You little...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.01,0:07:03.68,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,So broad-minded.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.68,0:07:05.18,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.16,0:07:10.35,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,No outside shoes allowed in the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.35,0:07:12.20,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Put on the slippers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.20,0:07:13.82,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.35,0:07:17.35,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while since I've \Nbeen in a high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.35,0:07:19.43,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.38,0:07:23.42,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,We usually meet at a coffee shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:24.93,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.93,0:07:29.63,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,When I heard that there were \Nfour demis at the same school,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.63,0:07:33.01,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I should at least see \Nthem, given my line of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:35.20,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Also, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.20,0:07:36.76,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Kurtz-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.52,0:07:40.77,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Did something happen \Nbetween you and him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.77,0:07:42.73,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.62,0:07:47.05,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Well... Sort of...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.29,0:07:53.33,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Just the fact that you and he touched \Nmakes my coming here worthwhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.33,0:07:54.76,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.76,0:07:56.28,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,You're infuriating!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.28,0:07:59.40,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,I can't give too many details, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.40,0:08:01.14,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Put your name and address here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.14,0:08:02.04,Default,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.03,0:08:05.80,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,So, what kind of work do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.80,0:08:06.25,Default,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,Gulp...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:08.45,Default,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,I-It has nothing to do with demi-humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.45,0:08:10.79,Default,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,Really, it has nothing to do \Nwith demi-humans at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.79,0:08:12.42,Default,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Not demi-humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.20,0:08:13.04,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, Kurtz is
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.04,0:08:16.07,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,our weapon against succubi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.07,0:08:17.74,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:22.66,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Stop trying to make this \Nsound like some anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.66,0:08:23.52,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.34,0:08:26.02,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,So, how have things been lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.47,0:08:27.91,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,You doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.91,0:08:29.38,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,How have things been?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.38,0:08:32.40,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Just like always. I'm getting by.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.40,0:08:35.03,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, I think you're doing great.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.52,0:08:37.64,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Given the depth of their natures,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.64,0:08:41.41,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,succubi generally either live apart from society
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.41,0:08:45.17,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,or just throw caution to \Nthe wind and live boldly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.72,0:08:50.50,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Usually, we police deal with the \Ntroublemakers in the latter category.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.74,0:08:55.74,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Among succubi, upright members \Nof society like you are rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.74,0:09:01.35,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, the government is facing the \Ntough situation succubi are currently in—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:03.85,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Smoke in the smoking room!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.90,0:09:08.65,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,I fully realize you consciously \Nlive as a functional adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.25,0:09:13.57,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't it about time you thought about \Nsettling down and starting a family?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.57,0:09:15.79,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,I can introduce you to some guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.79,0:09:17.24,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Where's this coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:19.20,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Nowhere special.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:23.25,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,It just makes me worry to see a \Nyoung woman living all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.03,0:09:27.44,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Especially you, having known \Nyou since you were little.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.44,0:09:30.19,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,You sound like a father, Ugaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.19,0:09:31.80,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling a father?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.16,0:09:36.77,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,But you do more fatherly things \Nfor me than my actual father.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.23,0:09:39.36,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't supposed to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.36,0:09:40.26,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.96,0:09:42.89,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Marriage, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.47,0:09:46.73,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, there is someone I'm interested in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.48,0:09:48.62,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.96,0:09:53.12,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that reaction?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.12,0:09:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who brought it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.31,0:09:56.90,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yeah, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.90,0:10:01.21,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,But you always make excuses \Nwhen this subject comes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.21,0:10:04.11,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Like you don't want to use your aphrodisiac \Neffect to get a boyfriend,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.11,0:10:06.16,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,or you don't know what real love is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.61,0:10:09.02,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought you'd find a man yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.02,0:10:10.33,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me touch you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.33,0:10:11.50,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.50,0:10:15.75,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Getting too worked up is \Nhard on a man my age!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.75,0:10:17.55,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph. Pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.55,0:10:21.01,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,The man I'm interested in doesn't \Nhave much sexual desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.01,0:10:23.55,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,My touch doesn't even affect him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.55,0:10:23.93,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.52,0:10:27.23,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.81,0:10:29.40,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Other than gays,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.40,0:10:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's no man your aphrodisiac \Neffect wouldn't work on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.27,0:10:37.20,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,But he... He didn't seem affected at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.20,0:10:39.44,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,That just means he didn't look affected.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.44,0:10:41.84,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,I bet he knows a lot about demis, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.84,0:10:43.26,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.26,0:10:47.29,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Even if your aphrodisiac effect \Ndid work on him,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.29,0:10:50.80,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,he was probably making \Nan effort not to show it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.80,0:10:52.42,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't look affected,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.36,0:10:54.75,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,but he really was?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.61,0:10:56.84,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,He really was?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.06,0:11:00.74,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Your aphrodisiac effect \Ndid its job on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.74,0:11:02.16,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't special!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.16,0:11:03.36,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Are you disappointed?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.36,0:11:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are your feelings for him real?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.48,0:11:08.10,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Can you still say you like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.25,0:11:12.06,Default - italics,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,When that happened, Takahashi-sensei
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.36,0:11:14.36,Default - italics,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,was affected by my aphrodisiac effect?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.36,0:11:18.03,Default - italics,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,He was excited by me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.17,0:11:23.68,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,I see, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.68,0:11:26.71,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,If you can believe that it's okay \Nto use your aphrodisiac effect,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.71,0:11:29.95,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,that would mean you truly love him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.95,0:11:32.37,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,W-Would it really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.72,0:11:34.28,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,I only took interest in Taka—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.28,0:11:38.82,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,in him to begin with because \Nwhen I touched his hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.82,0:11:42.76,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,there was no indication that he'd \Nfelt my aphrodisiac effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.16,0:11:47.39,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Learning that it really had affected \Nhim did excite me a little,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.39,0:11:50.73,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,but it contradicts the very reason \Nwhy I took interest in him...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.73,0:11:53.30,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Which means my excitement is transient,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.30,0:11:55.49,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,and can't be called the real thing, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.49,0:11:58.58,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure I read in a \Nromance how-to book that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.58,0:12:00.70,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,the beginning of love is often \Nmistaken or preconceived...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.70,0:12:06.32,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, as an educator, I feel that love \Ncarried by momentum is... is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.32,0:12:10.19,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,But... But if someone seriously \Npursued me, I'd...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.19,0:12:12.08,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,If a succubus fell under \Nan aphrodisiac effect...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.61,0:12:18.17,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't bear to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.17,0:12:19.05,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:24.05,Eyecatch,,0000,0000,0000,,Interviews with Monster Girls
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.04,0:12:27.30,Default,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I shouldn't have said that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.65,0:12:30.98,Default,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,I hope no one's figured out my \Nconnection with demi-humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.98,0:12:32.18,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Someone suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.18,0:12:33.05,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.05,0:12:34.42,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,What was he like?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.42,0:12:37.53,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he was huge, like a bear...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.53,0:12:38.11,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,A bear?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.40,0:12:40.48,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,And he had shaggy hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.48,0:12:41.44,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Shaggy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.73,0:12:44.61,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,And he had eyes like a beast, \Ntargeting its prey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.64,0:12:48.05,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I can't picture anything but a bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.05,0:12:50.49,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,But it looks like I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.80,0:12:54.75,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Sakki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.08,0:12:56.18,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you aren't her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.18,0:12:57.75,Default,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.75,0:12:59.31,Default - italics,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,It's that demi-human.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.31,0:13:00.42,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You're a foreigner?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.42,0:13:01.38,Default,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.38,0:13:04.23,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,We never see foreigners at this school!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.23,0:13:05.65,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You're even blond!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.65,0:13:08.36,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. They're very uncommon here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.36,0:13:10.14,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,So are we.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.90,0:13:12.55,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.17,0:13:15.21,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Your uniform's different, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.21,0:13:15.60,Default,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,Gulp!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.60,0:13:18.05,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I get it! You're transferring here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.05,0:13:20.98,Default,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Th-Th-That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.44,0:13:25.28,Default,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.13,0:13:28.32,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't look like he's transferring here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.32,0:13:29.67,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.53,0:13:33.37,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I mistake him for Sakki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:35.29,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,He's a boy, for one thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.29,0:13:37.36,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,He was acting a little suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.36,0:13:38.33,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Was he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.86,0:13:40.09,Default,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,That was too close.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.48,0:13:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think they almost started to suspect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.01,0:13:44.55,Default,Satake,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.86,0:13:46.16,Default,Ohkawa,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.16,0:13:47.01,Default,Satake,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.31,0:13:48.43,Default,Satake,0000,0000,0000,,Sexy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.43,0:13:48.76,Default,Ohkawa,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.10,0:13:52.35,Default,Ohkawa,0000,0000,0000,,But, Satake, isn't this peeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.35,0:13:54.08,Default,Ohkawa,0000,0000,0000,,Calling it a dirty trick is an understatement.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.08,0:13:55.48,Default,Satake,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.48,0:13:57.58,Default,Satake,0000,0000,0000,,The picture is sexy enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.58,0:13:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the real thing was even more intense!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.97,0:14:05.03,Default,Satake,0000,0000,0000,,Being hit by a succubus's... pheromones? \NI couldn't help it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:07.59,Default,Ohkawa,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of get how you feel, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.53,0:14:14.58,Default,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at Sakie-sensei \Nwith such lascivious eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.58,0:14:15.22,Default,Ohkawa,0000,0000,0000,,Wha?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.22,0:14:16.41,Default,Satake,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.41,0:14:18.50,Default,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a passing pol—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.65,0:14:20.95,Default,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,A passerby!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.95,0:14:22.38,Default,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,I meant specifically!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.75,0:14:26.13,Default,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,You took this... in secret, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.13,0:14:27.40,Default,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,How cowardly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.40,0:14:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a man, aren't you ashamed \Nto do things like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.09,0:14:32.65,Default,Ohkawa,0000,0000,0000,,You heard him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.40,0:14:35.85,Default,Satake,0000,0000,0000,,I do think what I did was pretty low.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.85,0:14:38.00,Default,Satake,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm a high school kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.00,0:14:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a healthy adolescent!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.08,0:14:43.70,Default,Satake,0000,0000,0000,,With a succubus like Satou-chan as a teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.70,0:14:45.94,Default,Satake,0000,0000,0000,,it's weirder to tell me not to take interest!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.94,0:14:47.28,Default,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because she's a succubus?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.50,0:14:53.20,Default,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,Are you interested in Sakie-sensei \Nbecause she's a succubus?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.66,0:15:01.82,Default,Satake,0000,0000,0000,,My taking that picture might have \Nhad something to do with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.82,0:15:04.48,Default,Satake,0000,0000,0000,,But even if she weren't a succubus,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.48,0:15:06.96,Default,Satake,0000,0000,0000,,I still think Satou-chan is cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.07,0:15:14.35,Default,Satake,0000,0000,0000,,I know that's kind of shady!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.11,0:15:21.02,Default,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,Good answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.30,0:15:23.84,Default,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,Try not to forget that feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.84,0:15:27.88,Default,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,Just this once, I'll give you \Npermission to keep that photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.72,0:15:31.75,Default,Satake,0000,0000,0000,,What was that about? He sure was weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.75,0:15:33.82,Default,Ohtomo,0000,0000,0000,,I think you were pretty weird, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.58,0:15:39.42,Default,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, where did Ugaki-san go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.16,0:15:39.87,BlackWhite,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Smoking Room
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.70,0:15:46.48,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,That's delicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.97,0:15:49.51,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.78,0:15:52.34,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hello... Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.34,0:15:54.91,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my name is Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.91,0:15:57.30,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Ugaki. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.30,0:15:59.31,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, Ugaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.72,0:16:00.64,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.68,0:16:02.48,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.48,0:16:04.32,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.84,0:16:07.30,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, so you smoke, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.30,0:16:08.90,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, occasionally.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:10.74,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Occasionally, eh? How often is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.12,0:16:15.92,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's been about two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.92,0:16:17.16,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,That's a little too occasional.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.84,0:16:20.42,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,What made you suddenly \Ndecide to smoke today?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.42,0:16:22.39,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Is today special?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.39,0:16:24.21,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.21,0:16:25.32,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.32,0:16:28.48,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I heard your work involves demi-humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.48,0:16:30.65,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Who told you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.65,0:16:31.94,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Was it Kurtz?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.94,0:16:32.84,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sort of.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:34.76,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.76,0:16:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's nothing worth hiding, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.33,0:16:40.97,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Kurtz and I work for what's called \Nthe "Demi-human Division."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.33,0:16:44.27,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! You're policemen from \Nthe Demi-human Division?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.27,0:16:45.69,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I've never met one before!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.94,0:16:48.51,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there aren't many demi-humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.51,0:16:52.22,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,which means incidents involving \Nthem are even rarer, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.22,0:16:54.11,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what kind of work do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.43,0:16:56.99,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,My work has nothing to do \Nwith demi-humans at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.30,0:16:58.37,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.37,0:16:59.49,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of expression is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.02,0:17:02.87,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Though, back in the day, I was pretty busy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.94,0:17:08.38,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,The world used to be a lot harsher \Ntoward demi-humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.61,0:17:11.84,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Since they had it rough both \Nsocially and psychologically,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.84,0:17:15.21,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,we'd often see demi-humans \Ncausing problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.21,0:17:17.39,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,But lately, you never hear of that happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.76,0:17:19.72,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Because the government took action?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.72,0:17:21.19,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,The guarantee system?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.19,0:17:22.93,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,That's probably part of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.93,0:17:26.90,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,but as a whole, society sort of mellowed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:29.04,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,I realized that again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.04,0:17:29.92,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Today?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.92,0:17:33.16,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,This school has three \Ndemi-human students, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.16,0:17:35.00,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't heard any bad rumors,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.00,0:17:38.85,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,but a part of me was scared to look into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.85,0:17:42.33,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,But once I actually did, I was \Nsurprised  by what I found.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.89,0:17:45.46,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,They look like they're having a great time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.46,0:17:48.78,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,It almost made me want to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.78,0:17:52.57,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,I started to think the world's \Nheading in a good direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.57,0:17:54.76,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure how they were raised is part of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.25,0:17:57.61,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,and they're probably blessed \Nwith good teachers, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.66,0:18:01.91,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I took your Demi-human Division job.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.30,0:18:03.57,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Bold words!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.31,0:18:11.69,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,But unfortunately, I have a job that \Nyou can never take from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.99,0:18:13.92,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.92,0:18:17.49,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,The majority of incidents \Ncaused by demi-humans
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.94,0:18:20.24,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,are incidents involving aphrodisiac effects.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.45,0:18:22.40,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Aphrodisiac effects?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.40,0:18:27.22,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,You mean incidents caused by succubi's \Naphrodisiac effects, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.22,0:18:30.25,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Let's say a succubus is molested.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.25,0:18:34.22,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't always true that the succubus used \Nher aphrodisiac effect accidentally.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.22,0:18:38.48,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Some of them intentionally \Nuse it to get molested.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.93,0:18:38.48,Default,Succubus,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Serves you right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.48,0:18:42.02,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Determining whether the succubus \Nused the aphrodisiac effect
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.02,0:18:45.48,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,deliberately is extremely difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.48,0:18:48.66,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,What teacher could actually steal that job?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.66,0:18:50.13,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.13,0:18:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.80,0:18:54.36,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,You mean there's a way to make the \Ncorrect judgment in those cases?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.82,0:18:57.95,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,There's no failsafe method.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.95,0:19:00.09,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,All we can do right now
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.09,0:19:04.01,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,is to maintain communication with \Nsuccubi in our jurisdictions,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.01,0:19:10.54,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,and determine in advance \Nif they're malicious or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.54,0:19:13.08,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I bet succubi don't like you much, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.48,0:19:17.87,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm basically interrogating them about \Nthings that may or may not happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.45,0:19:21.02,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,All I can tell them is that it's my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.02,0:19:23.09,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't like I want them to hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.65,0:19:26.16,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,So you haven't reached any compromise?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.24,0:19:32.40,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I do occasionally meet succubi I \Nget along with, for whatever reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.20,0:19:34.98,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,There's one rather unusual one...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.74,0:19:51.71,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I hear you're pretty \Nknowledgeable about demis.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.15,0:19:53.58,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.58,0:19:56.34,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,But you do know about \Nthe nickname "demis."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.41,0:19:59.67,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, take care of Sakie, will ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.94,0:20:02.55,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,What about the other demi-chans?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.57,0:20:05.02,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.02,0:20:08.74,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of all the demi-chans, \Nincluding Sakie,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.74,0:20:09.52,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.78,0:20:16.98,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best to make this a world \Nwhere demis can feel at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.44,0:20:21.50,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,You just do your best to look \Nafter each of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.50,0:20:24.95,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Give them lots of good memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.34,0:20:27.66,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Okay... You can count on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.98,0:20:39.42,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,When you interact with demis, is there \Nanything you're careful about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.72,0:20:44.43,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than try to make them like me, \NI try to make them not hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.67,0:20:49.14,BlackWhite,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Smoking Room
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.43,0:20:46.50,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,If being hated by girls is "100,"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.50,0:20:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and being hated by demis is "100,"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.14,0:20:52.97,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,then being hated by demi girls would \Nbe 100 x 100, which is 10,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.97,0:20:55.35,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,You can really express it \Nwith such simple math?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.35,0:20:57.15,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,It's only an example.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.15,0:20:58.86,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,That's just how complicated it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.37,0:21:03.24,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,You might find yourself distanced from \Nthem for surprising reasons, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.24,0:21:05.13,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't try to scare me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.13,0:21:06.56,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.56,0:21:07.49,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Speak of the devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:09.81,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Are you done talking now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.81,0:21:11.26,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.26,0:21:14.24,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hi there, little lady vampire.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.24,0:21:16.08,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,My name's Ugaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.08,0:21:18.76,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Takanashi Hikari, from class 1-B!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.76,0:21:20.98,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.98,0:21:22.51,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,"Little lady," he said!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.88,0:21:25.94,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.94,0:21:27.01,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.47,0:21:29.35,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sniff, sniff. Sniff, sniff.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.92,0:21:29.35,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.58,0:21:30.60,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You stink!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.37,0:21:33.81,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I hate cigarettes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.27,0:21:37.56,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I guess she's sensitive to cigarette smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.15,0:21:41.94,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,So, anyway, that's how I \Ndeal with demi-humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.34,0:21:45.69,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Occasionally, I go out to meet \Ndemi-humans out of my jurisdiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.69,0:21:49.94,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't think the police will have to \Ndo anything about those demi-chans.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.94,0:21:52.08,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that succubus.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.08,0:21:55.54,Default,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, I'll probably need to have \Nyou do some serious work for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.94,0:22:00.36,Default,Kurtz,0000,0000,0000,,Takoyaki is so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.74,0:22:05.05,Default - italics,Ugaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll smack him later...
